The paper proposes a place recognition algorithm for 3D data, which is a common problem in robotics and autonomous systems. The algorithm is based on segment matching, which involves both local and global features. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories, including Robotics (cs.RO), Computer Vision (cs.CV), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on robotics and autonomous systems, cs.RO is the most likely sub-category.
